  "text": "In addition to single-frame based pose annotations, we also record, annotate, and make available a fish action dataset. [CITATION_1] provides a comprehensive catalogue of zebrafish actions, from which a subset of 9 action classes are considered in this paper, which is listed below as well as illustrated in Surface: Moves up towards the water surface.",
